-- Palladio Finanziaria May Invest in Premafin, Il Sole Reports
-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2012-01-05T08:04:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/palladio-finanziaria-may-invest-in-premafin-il-sole-reports.html
Palladio Finanziaria, an Italian
investment firm, may buy a stake in  Premafin Finanziaria SpA (PF) ,
the company that controls insurer  Fondiaria-SAI SpA (FSA) , through a
capital increase,  Il Sole 24 Ore  reported without saying how it
obtained the information.  Sator SpA, the fund founded by Matteo Arpe, and 21
Investimenti, also are interested in Premafin, Sole said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
 ssirletti@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  